OL,2,MAn Internet for the Solar System
OL,4,CDavid Johnson
OL,5,CSun 10:40-11:10
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GThis talk explores the emerging
OL,9,Gconcept of “An Internet for the Solar
OL,10,GSystem” — a networked approach to
OL,11,Ginterplanetary communication that
OL,12,Gcould transform how spacecraft,
OL,13,Ghabitats, and missions share data
OL,14,Gbeyond Earth. Starting with NASA’s
OL,15,GLunaNet initiative, we will examine
OL,16,Ghow principles from terrestrial
OL,17,Ginternet infrastructure are being
OL,18,Gadapted for the unique challenges of
OL,19,Gspace: extreme latency, intermittent
OL,20,Gconnectivity, and vast distances. The
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
